A minimalistic illustration featuring four overlapping translucent circles in soft muted colors—warm amber, deep teal, dusty rose, and sage green—arranged in a Venn diagram formation against a clean cream background. At the center where all four circles intersect, a small glowing golden seed or ember radiates subtle warmth, symbolizing the sweet spot of purpose. The circles have delicate watercolor-like edges that bleed slightly into each other, creating organic harmony. Gentle shadow beneath gives the composition subtle depth. The overall feeling is contemplative, balanced, and aspirational—a quiet moment of alignment and clarity.
